there are three types of CSS:
1. Inline
2. Internal or Embeded
3. External

--- BASIC HTML PAGE----
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title> THIS IS GITHUB CSS NOTES</title>
      <!-- Stylesheet of web page -->
    <style></style>
</head>
 <body>
    <!-- Body section of web page -->
</body>
 </html>
 
 ------BASIC HTML WITH CSS STYLE-----
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>
        Simple webpage
    </title>
    <!-- Stylesheet of web page -->
    <style>
        body {
            text-align: center;
        }
        h1 {
            color: green;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>Welcome to JOECSTACY GITHUB</h1>
 
    <p>CSS NOTES </p>
</body>
 
</html>
